const appColors = {
    primary: '#1165EF', // blue
    text: '#0E1E2F',
    background: '#FFFFFF',
    surface: '#FFFFFF',
    destructive: '#F83E3E',
    success: '#409348',
    alert: '#FCAC12',
    lightGray: '#EBEEF1',
    medGray: '#DFDFDF',
    textGray: '#9CA3AF',
    ltPink: '#E7B4B4',
    ltBlue: '#A1AAF0',
    frcRed: '#F83E3E',
    frcBlue: '#1165EF',
    ltGreen: '#B2E2B7',
    bodyText: '#757F87',
    buttonInactiveBackground: '#E7E9EB',
};

appColors.contrastLight = appColors.lightGray;
appColors.contrastDark  = appColors.bodyText;

export default appColors;
